Uses of Package
com.skobbler.ngx

  • Packages that use com.skobbler.ngx 
    Package Description
    com.skobbler.ngx
    Contains classes needed for initializing the SKMaps framework.
    com.skobbler.ngx.map
    Constains classses needed to show the map and information on the map.
    com.skobbler.ngx.map.realreach
    Contains classes needed to for implement RealReach feature.
    com.skobbler.ngx.navigation
    Contains classes needed for making a turn by turn navigation.
    com.skobbler.ngx.poitracker
    Contains classes for tracking pois during navigation.
    com.skobbler.ngx.positioner
    Contains classes used for implementing a positioner.
    com.skobbler.ngx.positioner.logging  
    com.skobbler.ngx.reversegeocode
    Contains classes that are needed in order to make a reverse geocode.
    com.skobbler.ngx.routing
    Contains classes that are needed in order to make a route and information about the status of computed routes.
    com.skobbler.ngx.search
    Contains classes needed to make a search (Nearby search , Multistep search).
    com.skobbler.ngx.trail
    Contains classses needed to show trails
    com.skobbler.ngx.util
    Constains utility classes
  • Classes in com.skobbler.ngx used by com.skobbler.ngx 
    Class and Description
    SKCategories.SKPOICategory
    Specifies types of categories for an SKSearchResult.
    SKCategories.SKPOIMainCategory
    Specifies the main categories.
    SKCoordinate
    Stores information about a coordinate.
    SKMaps
    SKMaps provides support for general settings and management that concerns the whole SKMaps SDK.
    SKMaps.SKDistanceUnitType
    Distance unit type enum.
    SKMaps.SKLanguage
    Stores possible values for languages supported by the SDK.
    SKMapsDownloadListener
    Listener for download operations.
    SKMapsInitSettings
    Class that stores settings information for initializing the library.
    SKPrepareMapTextureListener
    Listener for events related to preparing map resources needed in order to inialize the library.
    SKProxySettings
    Class used for the proxy used by the framework for internet requests.
